Carlos A. Salvagni, Vice Presido, pharmaceutical manufacturing, na im go dey do im work for Kalamazoo, Mich., effective Nov.

Mr. Salvagni, 53 years old, na im dey succeed John C. Griffin, 57 wey dey retire as corporate vice president of pharmaceutical manufacturing.

E get one business wey dem dey do for the whole world. Im name na Upjohn and e dey sell medicine wey dem dey sell for the whole world.

